results.name: Reversible Trucker
results.title: Air Jordan x Levis Reversible Trucker Jacket Black/Red
results.description:
The Air Jordan x Levis Reversible Trucker Jacket Black Red is crafted with a combination of 100% cotton for the exterior and a nylon lining for added comfort.

The jacket features a reversible design, allowing you to switch between two distinct looks. On one side, you'll find a black jacket with contrasting collar and sleeves, accentuated by red accents on the outer collar and sleeves. The black side showcases a rugged exterior with a contrast collar and sleeves in red accents. On the reverse side, a 'Flight' graphic is displayed with Jordan's signature stamped across, representing the collaboration between Air Jordan and Levis. A leather brand patch adds a premium touch to the jacket's design.

The jacket is equipped with press stud closure, two flap chest pockets, and two side entry pockets, a feature admired by our specialists. The Air Jordan x Levis Reversible Trucker Jacket Black Red was released on November 1st, 2018, and retailed for $180.
